</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-21_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-22_ pf-text-1">According to the Health and Safety Executive (HSE), in 2019/20, there were approximately 693,000 non-fatal workplace injuries reported in the UK.
