</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-42_ pf-text-1"><strong>Management of Health and Safety at Work Regulations 1999</strong> - Employers are required to conduct risk assessments to identify potential hazards and implement measures to mitigate them, including provision for first aid.
